{"url": "https://people.com/food/favorite-halloween-candy-by-state/", "text": "With Halloween but a few weeks away, pillowcases are about to be filled to the brim with candy\u2014but how do you dish out sweets your local trick-or-treaters are hoping for?\n\nGiven that America spends $2.7 billion on candy this time of year, CandyStore.com took it upon themselves back in 2017 to collect 10 years ofHalloween sales data for every state. See the full list below.\n\nAlabama \u2013 Candy Corn\n\nAlaska \u2013 Twix\n\nArizona \u2013 Snickers\n\nArkansas \u2013 Jolly Ranchers\n\nCalifornia \u2013 M&Ms\n\nColorado \u2013 Milky Way\n\nConnecticut \u2013 Almond Joy\n\nDelaware \u2013 Life Savers\n\nFlorida \u2013 Skittles\n\nGeorgia \u2013 Swedish Fish\n\nHawaii \u2013 Skittles\n\nIdaho \u2013 Candy Corn\n\nIllinois \u2013 Sour Patch Kids\n\nIndiana \u2013 Hot Tamales\n\nIowa \u2013 Reese\u2019s Peanut Butter Cups\n\nKansas \u2013 Reese\u2019s Peanut Butter Cups\n\nKentucky \u2013 Tootsie Pops\n\nLouisiana \u2013 Lemonheads\n\nMaine \u2013 Sour Patch Kids\n\nMaryland \u2013 Milky Way\n\nMassachusetts \u2013 Sour Patch Kids\n\nMichigan \u2013 Candy Corn\n\nMinnesota \u2013 Tootsie Pops\n\nMississippi \u2013 3 Musketeers\n\nMissouri \u2013 Milky Way\n\nMontana \u2013 Double Bubble Gum\n\nNebraska \u2013 Sour Patch Kids\n\nNevada \u2013 Hershey Kisses\n\nNew Hampshire \u2013 Snickers\n\nNew Jersey \u2013 Skittles\n\nNew Mexico \u2013 Candy Corn\n\nNew York \u2013 Sour Patch Kids\n\nNorth Carolina \u2013 M&M\u2019s\n\nNorth Dakota -Hot Tamales\n\nOhio \u2013 Blow Pops\n\nOklahoma \u2013 Snickers\n\nOregon \u2013 Reese\u2019s Peanut Butter Cups\n\nPennsylvania \u2013 M&M\u2019s\n\nRhode Island \u2013 Candy Corn\n\nSouth Carolina \u2013 Candy Corn\n\nSouth Dakota \u2013 Starburst\n\nTennessee \u2013 Tootsie Pops\n\nTexas \u2013 Starburst\n\nUtah \u2013 Jolly Ranchers\n\nVermont \u2013 Milky Way\n\nVirginia \u2013 Snickers\n\nWashington \u2013 Tootsie Pops\n\nWest Virginia \u2013 Blow Pops\n\nWisconsin \u2013 Starbursts\n\nWyoming \u2013 Reese\u2019s Peanut Butter Cups\n\nDistrict of Columbia \u2013 M&Ms\n\nSurprisingly, the candy that finished first in the most states is candy corn, though the tri-colored treats are quite polarizing.\n\nWATCH: Food Hack: Make Candied Apples with Candy Corn\n\nOther unconventional winners include Oreos in West Virginia (how did a cookie make the candy list in the first place?) and Toblerone chocolate bars in Texas (it may have something to do with the state\u2019s colossal airports).\n\nAll in all, victory\u2019s never tasted so good.", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/lLmj7z1ML_2Dw_i-HHrF5jhGUYY=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Thank-God-Christmas-at-Keller-Ranch-1-111725-43a6c59788b744348f09a042e53dba86.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/MrtcNGcY13yEe5rngB9x0f2Kq98=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/its-the-great-pumpkin-charlie-brown-1-101725-a2a808c8f5844332b59d1ae040e0d9f7.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/GUnjXWl2XwmL3V2bc1BgL17wdd8=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/rachel-lynn-Orlando-Bloom-katy-perry-110925-3-c2c03fdd82d04757894af3132b79a53e.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/a3ODGbSWXaR8igyo2g3Za_JzK2U=/343x228/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/royals-halloween-costumes-tout-100522-2995d19d39f94800b481ccfabfc9590a.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/qJuw298RrOXeFf1nPXorphK-xJs=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Michael-Meyers-Chucky-JasonVoorhees-102125-tout-bc510b054355440981e1fc572c288f82.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/f44Fdp1vRZOSs3OYbJaZfUvQcgY=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/books-candy-pairings-103125-3e6543cf6239472d8fbef0a342bfedd1.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/H2LiMmNQUm1rcV-srSHA0OaDw5Y=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Jonathan-Bennett-Anand-Desai-Barochia-a-keller-christmas-vacation-110625-1-af0cb84436664d9dadc9078c6a419e42.jpg", "h